description: Strawberry Fields REIT LLC, a self-managed and self-administered real estate investment trust, engages in the acquisition, ownership, and leasing of skilled nursing facilities and other post-acute healthcare properties. Its portfolio consists of 79 healthcare properties with an aggregate of 10,426 licensed beds. These properties are located across Arkansas, Illinois, Indiana, Kentucky, Michigan, Ohio, Oklahoma, Tennessee, and Texas. The company is based in South Bend, Indiana.
